sources.description:
German spies, led by the ruthless Dr. Honecker, exploit a stolen shortwave transmitter to feed secret shipping routes to a Japanese submarine. FBI agent Lewis Dearholt, working alongside radio engineer Ann Patterson, spearheads a daring U.S. government operation: firing and shadowing the West Coastâ€™s top radio experts to infiltrate and dismantle the treacherous spy ring.

Original title: Submarine Alert (1943)  Alternative title: Interceptor Command

Director: Frank McDonald

Stars: Richard Arlen, Wendy Barrie, Nils Asther
